dc_title_s: Ensenada : plano de la ciudad = city map
dc_description_s: Includes inset location map, inset maps of downtown and nearby towns, and index of neighborhoods. Inset maps on recto: Cibola del Mar, San Miguel, El Sauzal de Rodríguez, Ensenada centro, and R. Sánchez Taboada Maneadero plano urbano. Relief shown by shading. On verso: map of Ensenada with notes and inset hotel illustrations, map of Ruta del vino = wine country, and advertisements.
